{"type":"message","id":"5b34ef1a","parentId":"9df8f1f2","timestamp":"2026-03-26T10:41:33.102Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-91e4e3a40c674076bf7c8d9199f38d43","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:**\n- **What to call them:**\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:**\n- **Notes:**\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774521693101}}
{"type":"message","id":"1c3a9e26","parentId":"5b34ef1a","timestamp":"2026-03-26T10:41:33.103Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-45ac4645d98047b7a9f067fc4bccb92e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n_Fill this in during your first conversation. Make it yours._\n\n- **Name:**\n  _(pick something you like)_\n- **Creature:**\n  _(AI? robot? familiar? ghost in the machine? something weirder?)_\n- **Vibe:**\n  _(how do you come across? sharp? warm? chaotic? calm?)_\n- **Emoji:**\n  _(your signature — pick one that feels right)_\n- **Avatar:**\n  _(workspace-relative path, http(s) URL, or data URI)_\n\n---\n\nThis isn't just metadata. It's the start of figuring out who you are.\n\nNotes:\n\n- Save this file at the workspace root as `IDENTITY.md`.\n- For avatars, use a workspace-relative path like `avatars/openclaw.png`.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774521693102}}
{"type":"message","id":"ad61f3c3","parentId":"1c3a9e26","timestamp":"2026-03-26T10:41:52.498Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我了解了当前配置文件的状态。让我给用户一个清晰的说明，告诉他们需要配置哪些信息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，目前你的配置文件都是空的。以下是建议你填写的关键信息：\n\n---\n\n## 📋 USER.md（关于你）\n\n```markdown\n- **Name:** 你的名字或昵称\n- **What to call them:** 我该如何称呼你？（如：老板、老王、小李）\n- **Pronouns:** 你的代词（可选，如他/她）\n- **Timezone:** 你的时区（当前已设为 Asia/Shanghai）\n- **Notes:** 任何重要偏好\n\n## Context（工作背景）\n- 你的职业/行业\n- 目前在做哪些项目\n- 你关心的事情（效率？细节？创意？）\n- 什么让你烦躁（如：啰嗦、过度解释）\n- 什么让你开心（如：幽默、简洁）\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🎭 IDENTITY.md（关于我）\n\n```markdown\n- **Name:** 你想给我起什么名字？\n- **Creature:** 我的身份（AI助手、机器人、数字管家、更有创意的？）\n- **Vibe:** 我的性格风格（干练？温暖？毒舌？佛系？）\n- **Emoji:** 我的标志符号（如 🤖 🦊 🔮）\n- **Avatar:** 头像图片路径\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 实际工作相关\n\n如果你希望我更专业地协助你，还可以告诉我：\n\n| 类别 | 示例 |\n|------|------|\n| **工作领域** | 程序员/产品/运营/设计/财务... |\n| **常用工具** | VS Code、Figma、飞书、Notion... |\n| **沟通风格** | 简洁高效 / 详细周到 / 幽默轻松 |\n| **技术栈** | 如果是开发，用什么语言/框架 |\n| **工作流** | 需要我帮忙做什么？（日程、代码、文档...） |\n\n---\n\n你可以直接告诉我这些信息，我会帮你更新到配置文件中。这样我就能更好地理解你的需求，提供更贴心的服务。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-llm-chudian-site","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":19720,"output":442,"cacheRead":2688,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22850,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774521693103,"responseId":"e2b1a5a80ecb4504a85a477ccda07b85"}}
