{"type":"message","id":"a6609f38","parentId":"a8142d21","timestamp":"2026-03-26T12:00:15.021Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我已经创建了 WiFi PHY 知识文件。现在让我回答主人的问题：\n\n1. 我是否有 WiFi 协议？\n   - 官方 IEEE 802.11 标准文档是需要付费购买的，我没有直接的协议文档\n   - 但我可以通过网络搜索和获取公开的技术资料来学习\n\n2. 我已经学习了什么：\n   - WiFi 6 和 WiFi 7 的核心技术\n   - PHY 层的关键特性\n   - 创建了学习笔记\n\n让我给主人一个清晰的回答。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"主人，关于 WiFi 协议：\n\n---\n\n## 📜 协议文档情况\n\n**官方 IEEE 802.11 标准**：\n- 需要**付费购买**，IEEE 有版权保护\n- 企业通常会购买，个人比较贵\n- 我没有直接的协议 PDF\n\n**但别担心**，我可以通过以下方式学习：\n\n| 来源 | 内容 |\n|------|------|\n| WiFi Alliance 白皮书 | 技术概述、特性说明 |\n| 芯片厂商文档 | Qualcomm/Broadcom/MediaKit 技术文档 |\n| MATLAB WLAN Toolbox | 仿真和协议实现参考 |\n| 学术论文 | 深入特定技术点 |\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 已完成学习\n\n我刚刚：\n1. 获取了 **WiFi 6 (802.11ax)** 和 **WiFi 7 (802.11be)** 的技术资料\n2. 整理了一份 **WiFi PHY 基础笔记** → `knowledge/wifi_phy_basics.md`\n\n**笔记内容**：\n- WiFi"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-llm-chudian-site","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1774526400542,"responseId":"9a52b4e9ce934a14987548fcf63efda5","errorMessage":"terminated"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1ca29558","parentId":"a6609f38","timestamp":"2026-03-26T12:00:37.917Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我已经创建了一个 WiFi PHY 基础知识文件。现在让我回答主人的问题。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"主人，整理好了 🤖\n\n---\n\n## 关于 WiFi 协议\n\n**官方 IEEE 802.11 标准文档是付费的**，IEEE 版权保护，企业通常购买。\n\n### 我目前的资源：\n\n| 类型 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 公开技术白皮书 | WiFi Alliance、芯片厂商 |\n| 技术概述文档 | Cisco、MathWorks 等 |\n| 学术资料 | 论文、技术博客 |\n\n### 如果你需要：\n\n1. **公司有协议文档** → 可以分享给我学习\n2. **公开资源** → 我可以继续搜索整理\n3. **特定模块** → 告诉我你关注哪个部分，我深挖\n\n---\n\n## 📚 我已整理的笔记\n\n创建了 `knowledge/wifi_phy_basics.md`，包含：\n\n- ✅ WiFi 代际对照表 (WiFi 4~8)\n- ✅ PHY 核心技术演进（调制、带宽、OFDMA、MIMO）\n- ✅ WiFi 7 新特性详解（MLO、Multi-RU、4K-QAM）\n- ✅ 验证工程师关注点（帧结构、MCS 表、验证要点）\n- ✅ 后续学习计划框架\n\n---\n\n**主人有具体的协议文档或者想深入哪个模块吗？** 比如：\n- OFDMA RU 分配机制\n- PHY 帧结构详解\n- 信道编码（LDPC/BCC）\n- MIMO 预编码原理\n\n告诉我方向，我继续深挖！📡"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-llm-chudian-site","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":38,"output":340,"cacheRead":37056,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37434,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774526417066,"responseId":"028f3704a41844419a7f83c829409caf"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0067c4cc","parentId":"1ca29558","timestamp":"2026-03-26T12:03:20.908Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\media\\inbound\\aMDU2ovekV---eec9205c-dadb-4bc3-80ef-a1d75cbe4614.ogg (audio/ogg; codecs=opus) | C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\media\\inbound\\aMDU2ovekV---eec9205c-dadb-4bc3-80ef-a1d75cbe4614.ogg]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths — they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b536646a5e0acc2a7ea5131cf6ae\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_1ccae7b676709a68164395f25738e3cf\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_1ccae7b676709a68164395f25738e3cf\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-03-26 20:03 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_1ccae7b676709a68164395f25738e3cf\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_1ccae7b676709a68164395f25738e3cf\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_1ccae7b676709a68164395f25738e3cf\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b536646a5e0acc2a7ea5131cf6ae]\nou_1ccae7b676709a68164395f25738e3cf: {\"file_key\":\"file_v3_00105_b77ea8fd-c67f-412f-a1bb-def3d03e299g\",\"duration\":5000}"}],"timestamp":1774526600897}}
{"type":"message","id":"a7a67e47","parentId":"0067c4cc","timestamp":"2026-03-26T12:03:32.637Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户发送了一条语音消息。我需要先转录这条语音消息，才能理解用户说了什么。\n\n音频文件路径是：C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\media\\inbound\\aMDU2ovekV---eec9205c-dadb-4bc3-80ef-a1d75cbe4614.ogg\n\n这是一个 opus 编码的 ogg 文件。我需要使用语音转录技能来处理它。\n\n让我检查可用的技能 - 我看到有：\n- voice-transcribe: 使用 OpenAI gpt-4o-mini-transcribe\n- elevenlabs-stt: 使用 ElevenLabs Speech-to-Text\n- openai-whisper-api: 使用 OpenAI Whisper API\n\n我应该使用 voice-transcribe 或 openai-whisper-api 来转录。让我读取 voice-transcribe 技能看看如何使用。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_500beba5ffd4407c91364da9","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/skills/voice-transcribe/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-llm-chudian-site","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":31773,"output":199,"cacheRead":2688,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34660,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774526600916,"responseId":"8eb9c919237342ecba2848390e5fb75a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"54fd867d","parentId":"a7a67e47","timestamp":"2026-03-26T12:03:32.647Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_500beba5ffd4407c91364da9","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: voice-transcribe\ndescription: Transcribe audio files using OpenAI's gpt-4o-mini-transcribe model with vocabulary hints and text replacements. Requires uv (https://docs.astral.sh/uv/).\n---\n\n# voice-transcribe\n\ntranscribe audio files using openai's gpt-4o-mini-transcribe model.\n\n## when to use\n\nwhen receiving voice memos (especially via whatsapp), just run:\n```bash\nuv run /Users/darin/clawd/skills/voice-transcribe/transcribe <audio-file>\n```\nthen respond based on the transcribed content.\n\n## fixing transcription errors\n\nif darin says a word was transcribed wrong, add it to `vocab.txt` (for hints) or `replacements.txt` (for guaranteed fix). see sections below.\n\n## supported formats\n\n- mp3, mp4, mpeg, mpga, m4a, wav, webm, ogg, opus\n\n## examples\n\n```bash\n# transcribe a voice memo\ntranscribe /tmp/voice-memo.ogg\n\n# pipe to other tools\ntranscribe /tmp/memo.ogg | pbcopy\n```\n\n## setup\n\n1. add your openai api key to `/Users/darin/clawd/skills/voice-transcribe/.env`:\n   ```\n   OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...\n   ```\n\n## custom vocabulary\n\nadd words to `vocab.txt` (one per line) to help the model recognize names/jargon:\n```\nClawdis\nClawdbot\n```\n\n## text replacements\n\nif the model still gets something wrong, add a replacement to `replacements.txt`:\n```\nwrong spelling -> correct spelling\n```\n\n## notes\n\n- assumes english (no language detection)\n- uses gpt-4o-mini-transcribe model specifically\n- caches by sha256 of audio file\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774526612644}}
{"type":"message","id":"d7a4c38f","parentId":"54fd867d","timestamp":"2026-03-26T12:03:41.132Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我需要使用 voice-transcribe 技能来转录音频。但是这个技能的路径是针对 macOS 的。我需要调整一下命令。\n\n让我先检查一下这个技能在 Windows 上的位置，或者直接尝试运行转录命令。\n\n在 Windows 上，uv 应该也可以使用。让我尝试运行转录命令。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_71e8a7dcde21465da24780d0","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"uv run ~/.openclaw/skills/voice-transcribe/transcribe \"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\media\\inbound\\aMDU2ovekV---eec9205c-dadb-4bc3-80ef-a1d75cbe4614.ogg\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-llm-chudian-site","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":32360,"output":138,"cacheRead":2688,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35186,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774526612648,"responseId":"370a6e10abb741d98c0b8362bc66d0a7"}}
