{"type":"message","id":"16a357e9","parentId":"3a226dbd","timestamp":"2026-03-26T12:03:50.808Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"uv 没有安装。让我尝试其他方式转录音频。我可以使用 OpenAI Whisper API 技能或者直接使用 Python 调用 OpenAI API。\n\n让我检查 openai-whisper-api 技能。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-2a54142dd1d2482a90c8ec7eb4f6d2d4","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/skills/openai-whisper-api/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-llm-chudian-site","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":32692,"output":118,"cacheRead":2751,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35561,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774526621827,"responseId":"chatcmpl-46b8624a-a4fb-9ebb-b082-9596a1e8ffeb"}}
{"type":"message","id":"73394d1e","parentId":"16a357e9","timestamp":"2026-03-26T12:03:50.817Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-2a54142dd1d2482a90c8ec7eb4f6d2d4","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: openai-whisper-api\ndescription: Transcribe audio via OpenAI Audio Transcriptions API (Whisper).\nhomepage: https://platform.openai.com/docs/guides/speech-to-text\nmetadata: {\"clawdbot\":{\"emoji\":\"☁️\",\"requires\":{\"bins\":[\"curl\"],\"env\":[\"OPENAI_API_KEY\"]},\"primaryEnv\":\"OPENAI_API_KEY\"}}\n---\n\n# OpenAI Whisper API (curl)\n\nTranscribe an audio file via OpenAI’s `/v1/audio/transcriptions` endpoint.\n\n## Quick start\n\n```bash\n{baseDir}/scripts/transcribe.sh /path/to/audio.m4a\n```\n\nDefaults:\n- Model: `whisper-1`\n- Output: `<input>.txt`\n\n## Useful flags\n\n```bash\n{baseDir}/scripts/transcribe.sh /path/to/audio.ogg --model whisper-1 --out /tmp/transcript.txt\n{baseDir}/scripts/transcribe.sh /path/to/audio.m4a --language en\n{baseDir}/scripts/transcribe.sh /path/to/audio.m4a --prompt \"Speaker names: Peter, Daniel\"\n{baseDir}/scripts/transcribe.sh /path/to/audio.m4a --json --out /tmp/transcript.json\n```\n\n## API key\n\nSet `OPENAI_API_KEY`, or configure it in `~/.clawdbot/clawdbot.json`:\n\n```json5\n{\n  skills: {\n    \"openai-whisper-api\": {\n      apiKey: \"OPENAI_KEY_HERE\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774526630816}}
{"type":"message","id":"009cf5c1","parentId":"73394d1e","timestamp":"2026-03-26T12:03:58.608Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我尝试使用这个脚本。但是这个脚本也是针对 Linux/macOS 的 bash 脚本。在 Windows 上我需要用其他方式。\n\n让我直接使用 curl 调用 OpenAI API 来转录音频。首先检查是否有 OPENAI_API_KEY 环境变量。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dae26eecb32941158f14351f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$env:OPENAI_API_KEY = $env:OPENAI_API_KEY; if ($env:OPENAI_API_KEY) { \"Key found\" } else { \"No key\" }"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-llm-chudian-site","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":34385,"output":106,"cacheRead":1280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35771,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774526630818,"responseId":"1cdd44b9612d4e1fb2dbb5a731a7ab33"}}
